text: Nazarkino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Maxyutovsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 220 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 5 km from Maxyutovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Nazarkino
